[{"id":"cdfec1a9640a860a0896e0924c41fffa","from":"Lookout Mobile Security","from_email":"feedback@email.lookout.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Action Required: Upgrade to iOS 7.0.6","date":"2014-02-28T23:03:23.000Z","formatted_date":"Feb 28, 2014","formatted_time":"11:03 PM","body":" Lookout notice\nhttps://www.lookout.com/ \n\nOn Friday, February 21st, Apple released iOS \nhttp://support.apple.com/kb/HT6147 \n7.0.6 which fixed a security vulnerability that allows attackers to intercept and alter user communications. For devices that aren't eligible to upgrade to iOS 7, Apple also released iOS \nhttp://support.apple.com/kb/HT6146 \n6.1.6 which fixes the same vulnerability.\n\n\nLookout sent a notification to your device on Friday when this update became available, but because of the seriousness of this security flaw, we wanted to remind all of our users to upgrade to iOS 7.0.6 (or 6.1.6) as soon as possible, if you haven't already.\n\n\nTo update your OS now:\n\n1. Go to your Settings app\n\n2. Tap General > Software Update\n\n3. Tap Download and Install to download the update.\n \n4. Tap Install when the download completes\n\n\nTo verify that your system is up-to-date, you can open the Lookout app and make sure there is a green checkmark next to \"Security.\"\n\n\nThis security update fixes an SSL vulnerability that allows for man-in-the-middle attacks. In this type of attack, an individual can impersonate a trusted website to install malware or steal valuable data - effectively intercepting information like passwords that are sent between yourself and the intended website.\n\n\nIf you didn't receive the update notification from Lookout, please make sure you have the latest version of Lookout installed and activated. You can download the latest version from the \nhttps://itunes.apple.com/us/app/lookout-backup-security-find/id434893913?mt=8 \nApp Store .\n\n\nThe Lookout Team\n\nhttps://www.lookout.com/?utm_source=internal&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=l4b_prod_email \nLearn more about Lookout \n\n(c) 2014 Lookout, Inc. \u2219 One Front St. Suite 2700 \u2219 San Francisco, CA 94111\n\nhttps://www.lookout.com/d/settings\nUnsubscribe  \u2219 \nhttps://www.lookout.com/legal/privacy \nPrivacy  \u2219 \nhttps://www.lookout.com/legal/terms \nTerms and Conditions \n\n\n \n","body_html":"<html><!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n\n\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n  <head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n    <title>Lookout notice</title>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <style type=\"text/css\">\n      #outlook a {padding:0;} body{width:100% !important; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; margin:0; padding:0;}\n      .backgroundTable {margin:0; padding:0; width:100%;}\n      img {text-decoration:none; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;} img a, a img {border:0px!important;}\n      span.autoLinks a {color: #ffffff!important; text-decoration: none!important;}\n      span.preheader {font-size: 0; line-height: 0; display: none;}\n      table {border-collapse: collapse;}\n      p {margin:0; padding:0; margin-bottom:0;}\n      .emailCopy p {margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;}\n      .emailCopy a, .emailArticleHeading a, .emailImageHeading a, .emailButtonHeading a, .emailHeadline a {color: #000000; text-decoration: none;}\n      @media screen and (max-device-width: 550px), screen and (max-width: 550px) {\n      \tbody {padding: 0px!important;width:100%!important;}\n      \t*[class=\"emailDisplayFullWidth\"] {width: 100%!important; min-width: 100%!important; max-width: 100%!important; border: none!important; height: auto;}\n      \t*[class=\"emailSection\"] {}\n      \t*[class=\"emailTopBar\"] {padding: 20px 20px!important;}\n       .emailHeadline-green { font-size:25px!important; line-height:35px!important;}\n       .emailHeadline-blue { font-size:25px!important; line-height:35px!important;}\n      .secondaryHeader-text { font-size:18px!important; line-height:28px!important;}\n      }\n</style>\n</head><body bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; min-width: 100%; width: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n  \n    <span class=\"preheader\" style=\"display:none!important;font-size:0;line-height:0;\"></span>\n    <table class=\"backgroundTable\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; width: 100%;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <table class=\"emailDisplayFullWidth\" width=\"620\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\n\n            <tr>\n  <td class=\"emailTopBar\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" width=\"100%\" style=\"padding-top: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; padding-right: 30px; padding-left: 30px; border-bottom: 6px solid #eee; text-align: center;\">\n    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100%!important;border-collapse:collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"color:#aeaeae;font-family:'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:1px;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;\" align=\"center\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.lookout.com/\" style=\"color: #3db249; text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n            <font color=\"#aeaeae\">\n              <img label=\"Logo\" class=\"logo\" src=\"https://www.lookout.com/static/ee_images/lookout-email-logo.png\" alt=\"Lookout Mobile Security Logo\" title=\"Lookout Mobile Security Logo\" height=\"40\" width=\"200\" style=\"display: block; text-decoration: none; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; border-width: 0;\" />\n            </font>\n          </a>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n            <tr>\n  <td height=\"10\">\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"mainEmailSection\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" valign=\"top\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%; max-width: 620px;\">\n    <table class=\"main\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" class=\"emailBody\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; font-size: 1.15em; line-height: 1.5em;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td align=\"left\" class=\"emailBody-text\" style=\"helvetica: neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; padding: 0 20px; text-align: left;\">\n          <font face=\"'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;\">\nOn Friday, February 21st, Apple released iOS <a class=\"green\" href=\"http://support.apple.com/kb/HT6147\"><strong>7.0.6</a></strong> which fixed a security vulnerability that allows attackers to intercept and alter user communications. For devices that aren't eligible to upgrade to iOS 7, Apple also released iOS <a class=\"green\" href=\"http://support.apple.com/kb/HT6146\"><strong>6.1.6</a></strong> which fixes the same vulnerability.<br>\n<br>\nLookout sent a notification to your device on Friday when this update became available, but because of the seriousness of this security flaw, we wanted to remind all of our users to <strong>upgrade to iOS 7.0.6 (or 6.1.6) as soon as possible</strong>, if you haven't already.<br>\n<br>\nTo update your OS now:<br>\n1. Go to your Settings app<br>\n2. Tap General > Software Update<br>\n3. Tap Download and Install to download the update.<br> \n4. Tap Install when the download completes<br>\n<br>\nTo verify that your system is up-to-date, you can open the Lookout app and make sure there is a green checkmark next to \"Security.\"<br>\n<br>\nThis security update fixes an SSL vulnerability that allows for man-in-the-middle attacks. In this type of attack, an individual can impersonate a trusted website to install malware or steal valuable data - effectively intercepting information like passwords that are sent between yourself and the intended website.<br>\n<br>\nIf you didn't receive the update notification from Lookout, please make sure you have the latest version of Lookout installed and activated. You can download the latest version from the <a class=\"green\" href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/lookout-backup-security-find/id434893913?mt=8\">App Store</a>.<br>\n<br>\nThe Lookout Team\n          </font>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <td height=\"10\">\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n\n            <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table class=\"footer\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"learn-more\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; width: 100%; max-width: 650px; font-size: 16px; text-align: left; border-top: 1px solid #e1e1e1; border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e1e1; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"middle\">\n          <span class=\"link\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: auto; text-align: left; color: #3db249; font-size: 1.2em; padding: 0; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://www.lookout.com/?utm_source=internal&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=l4b_prod_email\" class=\"green\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #3db249;\">Learn more about Lookout</a></span>\n        </td>\n\n      \n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n      <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"finePrint\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"finePrintCopy\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: auto; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; color: #bbb; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n          &#169; 2014 Lookout, Inc. \u2219 One Front St. Suite 2700 \u2219 San Francisco, CA 94111<br />\n          <span class=\"bold\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.lookout.com/d/settings\" class=\"grey\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #bbb;\">Unsubscribe</a> \u2219 <a href=\"https://www.lookout.com/legal/privacy\" class=\"grey\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #bbb;\">Privacy</a> \u2219 <a href=\"https://www.lookout.com/legal/terms\" class=\"grey\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #bbb;\">Terms and Conditions</a>\n</span>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n    